e se ve hoy en día, fue posterior.</span></span></div><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p></o:p></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">El General descansó allí algunos años, pero las cosas cambiaron con la caída de Juan Manuel de Rosas.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">Rosas había huído a Inglaterra, y allí falleció. </span></em></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">Sus detractores, (que no eran pocos) estallaron de alegría, (antes no lo habían hecho por temor a que volviera) y se dispusieron a mancillar cualquier símbolo Rosista que hubiese por allí.<o:p></o:p></span></em></span></div><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">Los enemigos de la Santa Federación, inmediatamente identificaron un símbolo importante : </span></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;"></span></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">El sepulcro del General Facundo Quiroga.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;">Llegaron en un momento a enlazar la estatua de ?La Virgen dolorosa?, que adorna el panteón, tratando de hacerla caer.</span><br /><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: large;"></span><br /><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vTD5yBFZZss/UpplQzCNvFI/AAAAAAAAAsc/YbM6lnQAp2o/s1600/virgen+dolorosa.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><span style="font-size: large;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vTD5yBFZZss/UpplQzCNvFI/AAAAAAAAAsc/YbM6lnQAp2o/s1600/virgen+dolorosa.png" /></span></a></div><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p></o:p></span><br /><span style="font-size: large;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; La "Virgen Dolorosa".</span><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">Esto fue impedido por las autoridades, pero era seguro que en algún momento, pasaría algo grave.<o:p></o:p></span></em></span></div><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p><em></em></o:p></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">Los restos de Quiroga estaban en peligro.<o:p></o:p></span></em></span></div><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">Entonces????. el misterio.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">El sepulcro apareció abierto, y el féretro del General, había desaparecido!<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">Algunos llegaron a festejar lo que creyeron una profanación en toda la regla. Pero la verdad nunca salió a la luz.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">La verdad es que el cadáver del General, nunca salió del cementerio. Eso no se hubiese podido ocultar. <o:p></o:p></span></em></span></div><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">Y tampoco fue profanado. No había rastros de violencia.<o:p></o:p></span></em></span></div><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">El enigma perduró casi 100 años.<o:p></o:p></span></em></span></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">Pero todo se sabe, en algún momento.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">Un señor de apellido ?Demarchi?, se había casado con Mercedes, la hija de Facundo Quiroga.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><span style="font-size: large;">Para evitar los ataques, construyeron una falsa pared en su panteón familiar (que aún hoy existe) , y lo escondieron allí.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">El problema fue que, al no haber mucho lugar??pusieron el </span></em></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;"></span></em></span><br /><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><em><span style="font-size: large;">ataúd parado!! (Con el cadáver de pie, aclaremos)<o:p></o:p></span></em></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div style="border-color: currentColor currentColor windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 1pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-element: para-border-div; padding: 0cm 0cm 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: currentColor; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div><span style="font-size: large;"></span><br /><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: large; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;">La familia Demarchi no permite que se toque el panteón. Solo aceptaron una ventana exploratoria para asegurarse que el General Quiroga sigue allí. Esto fue en 2005.</span></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times 